      <p>Some time available during work hours to complete coursework.</p>
      <p>The National Minimum Wage (NMW) for apprentices is £2.68 per hour from 1st October 2013. This applies to 16-18 year old apprentices and those aged over 19 in the first year of their Apprenticeship. For all other apprentices the National Minimum wage appropriate to their age applies. </p>
